WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Sarah hikes up a mountain trail before dawn.

00:03.500 --> 00:06.000
She sets up her portable easel as the sun begins to rise.

00:06.500 --> 00:09.000
"The mountains teach patience and reverence," Sarah reflects.

00:09.500 --> 00:12.000
She captures the majesty of the Sierra Nevada peaks.

00:12.500 --> 00:15.000
The painting comes alive with the changing light.